{"type": "article", "id": 28525, "title": "瓷器系列", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-22T06:53:43Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 13, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703121540Xoyw1KNc6WALx8Br.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>          </p>\n<p>这个名为 Liquid 的瓷制容器系列是皇家艺术学院学生 <a href=\"http://www.alissavolchkova.com/\">Alissa Volchkova</a> 的毕业设计，将两大生产工艺汇集在了一起：先将陶泥塑造成形，然后浇上染色的釉料等待它自然干燥。通过这种随机的制作方式，最终的成品也具有了不可控性。每一件容器不仅实用，还可以创造出变化无穷的堆叠造型，将诗意的诠释与工业的概念结合在了一起。Liquid 系列计划于皇家艺术学院的 <a href=\"http://www.rca.ac.uk/news-and-events/events/show-rca-2016/\">showRCA 2016</a> 展上展出，展览日期为 6 月 26 日至 7 月 3 日。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121538pisTmtjBYv9EMk7r.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5391198\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121538mTfjhHzKYdLMEcPk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69070905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031215399WHkLOb5w1Py0ZUQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031215398jDwCLz10RtJdEFI.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55378973\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}